                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <pre class="overflow-x-auto text-sm"><code><span class="code-comment">-- Navigate to path (URL-based navigation)</span>
RouteManager.methods.navigateToPath(self, ws_id, <span class="code-string">"/user/123?section=settings"</span>)

<span class="code-comment">-- Navigate back in history</span>
